:'''Esther:''' I'm catching up with some old girlfriends in a few days. It's been years since we last met up. I wonder... would they laugh at me for being out of touch with fashion?
:'''Esther:''' I've heard of you from Lead Researcher Asta. You seem to know a lot, and might have your own insights on fashion.
:'''Esther:''' Can I ask for your advice? ...Do you think I should dye my hair a different color?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} The current color is fine.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_300100106-->
::'''Esther:''' But I think it feels a little old-fashioned.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} What color would you like?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_300100108-->
::'''Esther:''' *sigh* I can't really decide...
:<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_300100109-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_300100109-->
