::'''Esther:''' Sigh. Thanks to this invasion, I have to re-arrange a lot of the files of our department.
::'''Esther:''' Young researchers nowadays never have the patience to organize things. Old people like me always have to stay behind to clean up the mess.
::'''Esther:''' Well... I'll ask Gunn to come in the even days of the week and Wen Tianweng to come in the odd days of the week!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_500010122_1286-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_500010122_1286-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I can help too!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500011906-->
:::'''Esther:''' Oh, what a good kid! Not many kids these days are as kind as you are.
:::'''Esther:''' Let me introduce myself first. I'm Esther from the Department of Insight. As you can see, I'm not a young researcher. I mainly take care of the filing.
:::'''Esther:''' If you have any questions about files of the Department of Insight, I should be able to help you.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You look very young.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500011910-->
:::'''Esther:''' Aww, that's sweet. Young people these days know how to talk.
:::'''Esther:''' Although I'm content with my age, I never skip a single step in my skincare routine.
:::'''Esther:''' I pay attention to all the fashionable things young people do. Just look at my lipstick color. It's quite special, isn't it? It's the latest matte lipstick from the Galaxy Luminous collection. It looks good, right?
